{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "", "eventName": "", "entryType": "EXTRA", "storyCode": "", "avgTag": "", "storyName": "開演", "storyInfo": "猩紅劇團因傀影而“覆滅”，\n也必將因傀影而重生。", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_RL_castlehall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“劇團喉舌”倒在了舞台上。"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "手中絲線散落一地，如同蛛網那般，密密麻麻。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他曾經以此操縱古堡機關，以及他那堆邪惡的玩偶。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但現在，隨著這位前劇團成員的隕落，一切都結束了。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傀影鬆了口氣。"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的半生被猩紅劇團所支配，而今，他再一次掙脫了劇團的枷鎖。"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“鬧劇已然落幕，該讓生活重新回歸平靜了。”"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傀影這樣想著。"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而......"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "燈光閃耀，幕布拉開。"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "舞台還在等待著什麼。"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他不由自主地取過喉舌的椅子，放在了舞台中央。"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他坐下，他思考，他沉默。"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“歌唱吧，歌唱吧。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個細小的聲音在他腦中迴響。"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“為了你自己。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個音節從傀影嘴唇間流出。"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個，又一個。"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "緊接著，是字詞，是唱段。"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "舞台不再沉默，主演放聲歌唱。"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽聞這悠揚的旋律，陰影中傳出了幾不可聞的聲響。"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們在應和，它們在歌唱。"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒地的報幕人也隨之爬起，丟棄了手中的絲線，走向自己在舞台上的位置。"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_291", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......演員已就位。", "name": "“劇團喉舌”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_291"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_291"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我也應，履行職責。", "name": "“劇團喉舌”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_291"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "暮落已經聽到了聲響，只要找到傀影，任務就大功告成了。"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他推開了大門。"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_RL_castlehall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gateopen"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_291", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喔，第一位客人。", "name": "“劇團喉舌”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_291"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這，你怎麼會......", "name": "暮落"}, "figure_art": "avg_4025_aprot2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_291"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩位遊子如今都回到了劇團的懷抱。", "name": "“劇團喉舌”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_291"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可喜可賀。", "name": "“劇團喉舌”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_291"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，我在此宣佈......", "name": "“劇團喉舌”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_291"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戲劇開幕。", "name": "“劇團喉舌”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_291"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "24_RL03", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "24_RL03", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 0.9, "yScaleTo": 0.9, "duration": 20.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在暮落眼中，往昔的夢魘於舞台上一一浮現："}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "趕車人揚起長鞭。"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "報幕人傲然挺立。"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "道具師校準器具。"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "燈光師呼來喝去。"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "廚師長磨刀霍霍。"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "管家沉默不語。"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劇作家埋頭書寫。"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“影子”飄忽不定。"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“刀舞”寒光閃爍。"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“白英花”滿面微笑。"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於劇團長本人，他正凝視著暮落。"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有劇團成員都藏在舞台的陰影裡，眼中紅光爍爍。"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唯一一位受到光芒照耀的，則是“血鑽”盧西恩。"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他清了清嗓子。"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他正......"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "準備歌唱。"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}